gText_Birch_Welcome::
	.string "Oh, thank Arceus, a Pokémon Ranger\n finally answered our distress call!\p"
	.string "I am Professor Birch, and I lead the\n village here on the mountain.\p"
	.string "The last few years have been rough,\n with Silph Co shutting its doors, \p"
	.string "the Pokémon Centers have closed,\n and the Marts are depleted of supplies.\p"
	.string "All I have left to defend our town\n from the wild mountain is Psyduck. \p"
	.string "$"

gText_Birch_Pokemon::
	.string "This is what we call a Psyduck.\p"
	.string "\n"
	.string "$"

gText_Birch_MainSpeech::
	.string "The wild Pokémon on Kava Mountain have\n been growing aggressive lately.\p"
	.string "With Pokémon Trainers running out of\n resources, getting help has been,\p"
	.string "impossible\p"
	.string "I have begun research into medicinal\n plants on Kava Mountain.\p"
	.string "I think the plants might be the secret\n to being able to recover our strength.\p"
	.string "It has only been 10 years since the\n great Silph Co company closed,\p"
	.string "but the world has fallen to lawlessness\n and madness none the less.\p"
	.string "Now, wild Pokémon are more fearsome,\n power consolidates in those who horde\p"
	.string "resources and rule the streets of\n broken cities with fear.\p"
	.string "We have no idea how to survive out here.\n I prayed for you Rangers to return.\p"
	.string "The Aeros Region has fallen into an\n apocalyptic nightmare, and only you \p"
	.string "can help restore the balance; and my\n research can help you.\p"
	.string "I can't leave my town unprotected, so\n look for my Psyduck as you explore.\p"
	.string "Meet me in Kava Village, it's located at\n the base of the Mountain.\p"
	.string "$"

gText_Birch_AndYouAre::
	.string "Who should I be looking for?$"

gText_Birch_BoyOrGirl::
	.string "Are you a boy?\n"
	.string "Or are you a girl?$"

gText_Birch_WhatsYourName::
	.string "Alright quickly, the connection is\n failing.\p"
	.string "What's your name?$"

gText_Birch_SoItsPlayer::
	.string "The Ranger {PLAYER}{KUN}?$"

gText_Birch_YourePlayer::
	.string "What was that?!\p"
	.string "The ground is shaking Ranger\n {PLAYER}{KUN}\p"
	.string "I'm going to lose connection!\l"
	.string "Please help us!!\p"
	.string "$"

gText_Birch_AreYouReady::
	.string "You Rangers have been gone awhile\n"
	.string "the Aeros Region has changed\p"
	.string "You'll be facing fierce Pokemon\n"
	.string "criminals and bandits,\l"
	.string "and I fear something much worse\p"
	.string "Please hurry, I will see you in my Lab.\n Make haste Ranger {PLAYER}{KUN}.\p"
	.string "$"
